{{item:3025}} {{item:2051}} {{item:3065}} {{item:3009}} {{item:1031}} {{item:1011}} 

He has no damage what so ever yet you would think a 14 7 22 brand would smash a 5 9 17 tahm.
Nope. I could not kill him. I could not kite him and it took three of us too kill him.
How is this even balance Rito?
How much more magic pen do I need to actually make a difference when facing a tank?
Does Rito think that the current state of this horrible mata is good where a non damage champ who is so far behind can still take down a carry with ease and walk away with more than half health?

Maybe with more armor/magic resist item, the less damage your abilities do forcing tanks to actually build damage. Think of it as negative returns.
Or maybe buff the penetration items to actually make tanks think about their build instead of cookie cutter build = broken OP tank
